    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="Do I have to take on all the requests I receive?" class="article-title">
          Do I have to take on all the requests I receive?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p><span>You can decide which requests you wish to take on upon considering the content, the price offered, and your schedule.<br>If you can't accept a request, click "Decline".<br>Please note that the request will be automatically canceled once the response deadline has passed.<br><br>You do not necessarily have to accept all the requests you get.<br>Both the creator and fans will not be penalized when the creator does not accept a request.<br>Feel free to choose which requests to take on.</span></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

